1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:57,300 --> 00:01:01,940
(Liu's Herbal Shop)

3
00:01:04,420 --> 00:01:06,340
(Hongyun Gate)

4
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:07,640
Xiaojiu,

5
00:01:07,719 --> 00:01:08,640
what are the odds?

6
00:01:08,760 --> 00:01:09,480
Shoot it down?

7
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:10,280
A hundred percent.

8
00:01:13,079 --> 00:01:14,959
But saving someone in full view...

9
00:01:15,959 --> 00:01:16,879
I'm not confident.

10
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,680
The weapon Wu Xin used
to kill Jia Yi

11
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:25,079
was his usual dagger.

12
00:01:25,359 --> 00:01:26,599
Engraved with "Wu."

13
00:01:27,380 --> 00:01:28,660
(Wu)

14
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,040
First, save Xiaotao.

15
00:01:34,719 --> 00:01:38,040
If Li Xiaoshou finds Wu Lian's
proof of guilt, he's dead.

16
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,560
Master,

17
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:02,200
the golden thread for the
Princess Consort's gown is ready.

18
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:11,500
=Episode 13=

19
00:02:37,340 --> 00:02:41,900
(Hongyun Gate)

20
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,280
Stay sharp.

21
00:02:44,759 --> 00:02:45,560
Yes.

22
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:50,520
If all we wanted was to kill Wu Lian,

23
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,400
we wouldn't go through all this.

24
00:02:52,719 --> 00:02:54,680
Remember what Lady Cheng'en told you?

25
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:57,800
Rulan, you must aim to

26
00:02:58,479 --> 00:03:00,360
tear off Wu Lian's ugly mask

27
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:02,639
and expose his crimes to the world.

28
00:03:04,479 --> 00:03:05,000
Right.

29
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,400
We won't let Lady Cheng'en down.

30
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:12,580
(Liu's Herbal Shop)

31
00:03:13,719 --> 00:03:15,159
Brothers, drink up!

32
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,280
Come on, fill it up.

33
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:22,000
How's it going? All ready?

34
00:03:22,479 --> 00:03:23,400
I've arranged

35
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,039
for Yehu Gang brothers
to back us up.

36
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,560
I also prepped this.

37
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:29,080
Guaranteed foolproof.

38
00:03:29,479 --> 00:03:30,280
Don't worry.

39
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,639
I promised you.

40
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:33,240
I will save Xiaotao.

41
00:03:34,919 --> 00:03:36,280
All of you, be safe.

42
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:38,199
Drink!

43
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,400
Good wine.

44
00:03:42,639 --> 00:03:43,439
Who's there?

45
00:03:44,520 --> 00:03:45,319
Halt!

46
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,919
Oh, it's Mr. Feng.

47
00:03:50,879 --> 00:03:52,400
Found some good wine today?

48
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:56,000
Better than ours.

49
00:04:16,360 --> 00:04:17,160
Xiaotao!

50
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,519
Come.

51
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,199
Go!

52
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,399
Feng Da, go!

53
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:56,600
(Hongyun Gate)
After them!

54
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,500
(Hongyun Gate)

55
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:00,839
Move!

56
00:05:02,399 --> 00:05:03,240
Get back!

57
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:05,759
Move aside!

58
00:05:06,519 --> 00:05:07,279
Go away!

59
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:14,279
Quick!

60
00:05:14,279 --> 00:05:14,759
Get in!

61
00:05:14,759 --> 00:05:15,040
Go!

62
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,160
Huang Jiaojiao?

63
00:05:26,360 --> 00:05:27,160
Retreat.

64
00:05:33,639 --> 00:05:36,000
Master, they took Xiaotao.

65
00:05:36,519 --> 00:05:37,639
Took her?

66
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,879
Do you know where?

67
00:05:40,399 --> 00:05:41,680
They're all hiding at Silk Thread.

68
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:43,040
I found them.

69
00:05:43,319 --> 00:05:44,480
Silk Thread...

70
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:47,759
Huang Jiaojiao.

71
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,079
Go,

72
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,600
tell Wang Lu

73
00:05:50,759 --> 00:05:52,879
he can claim his reward
from Magistrate Yu.

74
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,360
Yes.

75
00:05:58,959 --> 00:05:59,759
Ms. Huang!

76
00:06:00,360 --> 00:06:01,319
What's the meaning of this?

77
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:02,319
What's this?

78
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:04,800
Barging in at midnight?
That'll be twenty taels.

79
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:06,560
You're suspected of hiding fugitives.

80
00:06:07,319 --> 00:06:09,680
Search everywhere. Leave no spot.

81
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,560
Tell them to be gentle!

82
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:12,920
These are fine fabrics!

83
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:15,360
Better worry about yourself.

84
00:06:17,800 --> 00:06:18,639
Quick, over here.

85
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,399
Captain, nothing.

86
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,199
How is that possible?

87
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,079
Could it be

88
00:06:25,079 --> 00:06:26,639
Wu Xin gave false info?

89
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:27,720
Pull out.

90
00:06:29,199 --> 00:06:30,279
This is official business.

91
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:33,240
I don't care what it is. Pay me!

92
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:34,000
Pay up!

93
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,519
Woman, you're obsessed with money!

94
00:06:35,759 --> 00:06:36,560
What?

95
00:06:37,199 --> 00:06:38,240
They weren't there?

96
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:40,680
No. We searched front and back.

97
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:41,839
No signs of hiding.

98
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:44,639
Huang Jiaojiao wasn't nervous at all.

99
00:06:46,519 --> 00:06:48,160
They must have just fled.

100
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,199
They can't be far.

101
00:06:51,199 --> 00:06:52,000
I'll search again.

102
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,759
Xin.

103
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:54,920
Forget it.

104
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:58,399
They probably have another plan.

105
00:06:58,680 --> 00:07:00,480
What matters most right now?

106
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:01,839
The Flower Festival.

107
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:03,639
Keep an eye on Silk Thread.

108
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,199
If anything moves,

109
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,279
report at once.

110
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:06,959
Yes.

111
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,480
Wan,

112
00:07:14,199 --> 00:07:15,839
come to the manor with me tomorrow.

113
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:19,519
But the Princess Consort's
gown isn't finished.

114
00:07:19,519 --> 00:07:21,959
Exactly why we need
a safe place to finish it.

115
00:07:24,160 --> 00:07:27,399
Your friend has some of
my cleverness.

116
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:32,240
In Jinxiu City, no one
outsmarts you, Master.

117
00:07:49,980 --> 00:07:54,140
(To win the Prince back,
cut the phoenix.)

118
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,959
It's me.

119
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,079
Xiaotao is weak.

120
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:22,279
I thank you for her.

121
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,200
Miss Xiaotao,

122
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:36,279
are you the daughter of the Huang family

123
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,639
from the south of the capital?

124
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:40,759
How do you know?

125
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:42,639
Your father is Huang Zhengxing.

126
00:08:43,720 --> 00:08:45,240
Your mother is from the Hong family.

127
00:09:06,519 --> 00:09:07,320
Xiaotao,

128
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,360
I'm your sister.

129
00:09:11,519 --> 00:09:12,320
Sister?

130
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:13,840
My sister?

131
00:09:16,519 --> 00:09:18,759
Mother sent you to
Yanyu Embroidery House.

132
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:22,039
And all you sent back
was a handkerchief.

133
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:25,879
Ms. Huang,

134
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:27,960
you, too?

135
00:09:34,559 --> 00:09:35,799
If I'm not mistaken,

136
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,679
you're the embroiderer
who was driven to death,

137
00:09:38,519 --> 00:09:39,480
Lin Rulan.

138
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,080
No wonder there are rumors

139
00:09:43,399 --> 00:09:45,879
that the manor's Lady Cheng'en
isn't really a Lady.

140
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:47,960
It's a long story.

141
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:50,399
Heaven saved me from death.

142
00:09:52,159 --> 00:09:55,600
We share the same enemy.

143
00:10:01,799 --> 00:10:02,600
Xiaoshou.

144
00:10:05,399 --> 00:10:06,399
What happened?

145
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:11,399
Mr. Feng held off the pursuers...

146
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,159
He's dead.

147
00:10:17,639 --> 00:10:19,840
Feng Da died saving me?

148
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:23,159
Impossible. Feng Da was

149
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:26,679
one of the toughest fighters
in the underworld.

150
00:10:27,320 --> 00:10:30,519
I saw it. He was covered in blood.

151
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,360
The soldiers took his body.

152
00:10:32,679 --> 00:10:33,960
Wu Lian arranged it all.

153
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:37,399
Otherwise, before the crime
was even proven,

154
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:40,000
Magistrate Yu wouldn't
have killed him.

155
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:40,759
Wu Lian...

156
00:10:41,919 --> 00:10:42,879
I won't rest

157
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:44,840
until you're dead.

158
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:20,020
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

159
00:11:20,260 --> 00:11:23,260
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

160
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:27,220
♪The past no longer binds♪

161
00:11:27,700 --> 00:11:31,420
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

162
00:11:31,860 --> 00:11:35,980
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

163
00:11:36,820 --> 00:11:39,700
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

164
00:11:40,060 --> 00:11:42,060
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

165
00:11:42,060 --> 00:11:46,140
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

166
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:48,740
♪For your faith that never broke♪

167
00:11:48,940 --> 00:11:53,060
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

168
00:11:53,940 --> 00:11:55,860
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

169
00:11:55,860 --> 00:12:00,100
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

170
00:12:01,300 --> 00:12:03,780
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

171
00:12:03,900 --> 00:12:06,540
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

172
00:12:06,540 --> 00:12:09,140
♪One thought turns into ash♪

173
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:15,460
♪No future left to write♪

174
00:12:16,540 --> 00:12:18,340
♪If I never fall♪

175
00:12:18,380 --> 00:12:20,740
♪How could this waiting end♪

176
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:22,100
♪If I bear no scars♪

177
00:12:22,100 --> 00:12:24,420
♪How could I challenge fate♪

178
00:12:24,420 --> 00:12:26,780
♪I knew there was no way back♪

179
00:12:26,780 --> 00:12:30,780
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

180
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:33,020
♪For your faith that never broke♪

181
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:37,180
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

182
00:12:38,140 --> 00:12:40,060
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

183
00:12:40,060 --> 00:12:44,460
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

184
00:12:45,540 --> 00:12:48,140
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

185
00:12:48,180 --> 00:12:50,740
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

186
00:12:50,740 --> 00:12:53,100
♪One thought turns into ash♪

187
00:12:54,220 --> 00:12:59,460
♪No future left to write♪

188
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:02,740
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

189
00:13:04,020 --> 00:13:06,140
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

190
00:13:07,820 --> 00:13:10,020
♪If we meet again someday♪

191
00:13:10,460 --> 00:13:16,260
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
